snippet.title: Harvest VR - The long awaited one
snippet.description:
Another huge update for Harvest VR. We're introducing a new part of the mine, buyable sprinklers, decoration mode and much more has changed in this update! Check these features (and more) out now and stay in touch for more updates!

Download the alpha now on Sidequest!
https://sidequestvr.com/app/1014/harv...​

Music in this video is from Zapsplat.

Join our discord!
https://discord.gg/mM2UsAF
